dubstep.solution.plan

Class Selection

  • java.lang.Object
    • dubstep.solution.plan.Operator
      • dubstep.solution.plan.Operator.Unary
        • dubstep.solution.plan.Selection

  • public class Selection
extends Operator.Unary
    A concrete implementation of a relational plan operator representing a selection operator. A selection has only a single feature: an Expression that evaluates to a boolean value when evaluated (e.g., Ship.Name = 'Enterprise').
